warning.p:
In , do not try to simplify 
		80 \cdot 6^{0.03x} \rightarrow 480^{0.03x}~~ \blert{\text{ Incorrect!}}
Remember that the order of operations tells us to compute the power 6^{0.03x} before multiplying by 80.

